snippet.title: Whitewater Wipeout Nonsense Video!
snippet.description:
🌊SURFERS REJOICE🌊

Hit the waves and ride the gnar in Whitewater Wipeout from Chuhai Labs! Jump, spin, crank, repeat in this all new, extreme surfing experience. Coming soon ONLY on the ultimate console on the go: the Playdate!
